snippet.title: Sulfur - Official Gameplay Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2023
snippet.description: Check out gameplay and more in this latest trailer for Sulfur, an upcoming modern old-school action-adventure game. In Sulfur, outsmart enemies, find treasure, improve weapons, harness powers. Delve deeper, find answers, and make it end.
